As emissions from African transport surge, a drastic rise in vehicle ownership, a growing population, increased urbanization, and a rising middle class. governments are finding ways to encourage a shift to cleaner, healthier electric vehicles. Sub-Saharan Africa and other developing countries urgently need a transport alternative to stave off the growing burden of fuel dependency and subsidies, as well as an electricity storage solution to leverage their abundant renewable energy resources. We've leveraged old methodologies with new technologies to come up with a better way of conducting leak inspections. Description: Jubilance is a sisterhood of women on a mission to make PMS mood swings a thing of the past.
Full Description: Kathy Cash and her husband Alan ran a small family business selling a lesser-known nutritional supplement called oxaloacetate. They sold oxaloacetate mostly to doctors, who recommended it to their patients for a number of different symptoms. Doctors began to report that their female patients were experiencing a curious “side effect” after taking oxaloacetate: life-changing relief from PMS mood swings. Alan was pleasantly surprised to hear the news, but then went about his day. As a woman, Kathy knew this wasn’t just a nice side benefit, it was a monumental discovery could transform the lives of millions of women. They both knew the cause needed a woman champion, so Kathy struck out on her own to launch a new brand, Jubilance, with a mission to make PMS mood swings a thing of the past. After multiple placebo-controlled clinical trials showing Jubilance provides dramatic reductions in PMS-related anxiety, gloominess, irritability and stress, Jubilance has become one of the fastest-growing women’s health brands in the U.S.

Description: Fledge - a Linux Foundation IIoT project connecting all machine data to any destination(s), enabling advanced sensor to cloud applications.
Full Description: Hosted by the Linux Foundation, Fledge is an open source framework and community for the industrial edge focused on critical operations, predictive maintenance, situational awareness and safety. Fledge is architected to integrate Industrial Internet of Things (IIoT), sensors and modern machines with the cloud and existing “brown field” systems like historians, DCS (Distributed Control Systems), PLC (Program Logic Controllers) and SCADA (Supervisory Control and Data Acquisition). All sharing a common set of administration and application APIs. Fledge developers and operators no longer face complexity and fragmentation issues when building data management  and/or advanced AI/ML IIoT applications and services.  Reliably gathering, processing, alerting, forwarding and managing sensor to cloud data is now easy, open and deployed.   Industrial users and equipment providers can continue to automate and transform their plants, mines and factories.  Fledge’s modern pluggable architecture eliminates the data silos often found in operational data systems. By using a consistent set of RESTful APIs to develop, manage and secure IIoT applications, Fledge is a unified industrial data solution.

Description: Residential developer that specializes in 3D printed concrete walls
Full Description: R Squared Texas is a dynamic construction company committed to transforming communities through cutting-edge construction practices and a strong focus on innovation. Our mission is simple: we leverage and integrate proven construction methods with innovative 3D concrete printing technology to develop high-quality, attainable homes. Under the leadership of CEO Jason Jones and COO Chris Knotts, we strive to introduce and expand the use of this technology across the industry and the current labor force to create the greatest impact. We firmly believe in pushing the capabilities of 3D printed technology to establish a sustainable and cost-effective model that supports the highest quality of homes. Our approach is grounded in combining the best of both worlds. We follow in the footsteps of tried and true code-compliant construction methods, supplementing them with our vastly more accurate equipment, methods, and materials. This allows us to provide a product that is better, faster, and stronger. By embracing the precision and efficiency of 3D concrete printing, we enhance construction outcomes and exceed traditional standards. At R Squared Texas, we offer a comprehensive range of services to meet the diverse needs of our clients. From development and home print subcontracting to licensing agreements, sales and distribution agreements, and research and development, we deliver integrated solutions that ensure high-quality construction, cost efficiency, and community-driven development. Our expertise extends to prefabricated panels, underground infrastructure, master community planning, home interiors, proprietary printers and materials, as well as marketing and online advertising. We are committed to pushing the boundaries of traditional construction practices. By leveraging advanced technologies and a talented team, we strive to create sustainable, efficient, and visually striking structures. Our dedication to quality extends beyond the construction process itself; we aim to deliver homes that provide comfortable and safe living environments, fostering a sense of pride and belonging for homeowners. R Squared Texas believes in construction that not only creates remarkable structures but also fosters the growth of the surrounding community. Through our transformative construction projects, we aim to enhance the lives of individuals and contribute to the growth and development of communities, leaving a lasting impact on the built environment. Join us in our mission to revolutionize the construction industry, making high-quality, attainable homes a reality. Together, we can shape communities, push the boundaries of technology, and establish a sustainable future for generations to come.
